column1: US-63 - As a User, I want to logout of my account, so that I can securely end my session and maintain account privacy.
US-62 - As a User, I want to update my account information (name, phone number ) and credentials, so that I can keep my account details accurate and ensure smooth communication.
US-61 - As a User, I want to login to my account, so that I can access member-specific features and manage my account information.
US-60 - As a Seller, I want to confirm incoming orders (if applicable), so that the order fulfillment process can begin.
US-59 - As a Seller, I want to delay incoming orders (if applicable), so that I can manage situations where stock is unavailable or the order cannot be fulfilled.
US-58 - As a Seller, I want to track the details of individual orders, so that I can access specific order information for processing and communication.
US-57 - As a Seller, I want to track the status of customer orders, so that I can monitor the order fulfillment process and identify any potential delays.
US-56 - As a Seller, I want to view customer order history, so that I can understand customer buying patterns and manage inventory more effectively.
US-55 - As a Seller, I want to update order tracking information for customers, so that I can keep them informed about the delivery progress of their purchases.
US-54-As an Admin, I want to prohibit user accounts that violate terms of service, so that I can uphold the store's policies and maintain the integrity of the system.
US-53 - As an Admin, I want to access and analyze store statistics and data, so that I can gain valuable insights into customer behavior and make informed business decisions.
US-52 - As an Admin, I want to view and update the store's general information, so that I can maintain accurate details about the store (name, contact information, etc.).
US-51-As an Admin, I want to create new staff accounts with specific roles and permissions, so that I can assign appropriate levels of access and functionality based on staff responsibilities.
US-50 - As an Admin, I want to view and manage all user accounts (Member, Manager, Staff), so that I have complete control over user access and system security.
US-49 - As a Post Staff, I want to view and manage user reports on posts, so that I can ensure a safe and positive online community for our customers.
US-48 - As a Post Staff, I want to delete inappropriate or offensive comments, so that I can maintain a safe and welcoming online environment.
US-47 - As a Post Staff, I want to reply to user comments on store posts, so that I can address customer inquiries and build relationships.
US-46 - As a Post Staff, I want to verify and approve user comments before they are displayed, so that I can ensure a positive and respectful online community.
US-45 - As a Post Staff, I want to edit and update existing store posts, so that I can maintain accurate and relevant information.
US-44 - As a Post Staff, I want to create informative and engaging posts for the store, so that I can educate and connect with customers on topics related to pregnancy, motherhood, and baby care.
US-43 - As a Product Staff, I want to delete  products, so that the store maintains a clean and accurate product catalog.
US-42 - As a Product Staff, I want to view and manage the complete product list, so that I can easily monitor product availability and make necessary adjustments.
US-41 - As a Product Staff, I want to manage product stock levels and quantities, so that I can prevent stockouts and maintain optimal inventory levels.
US-40 - As a Product Staff, I want to update existing product information, so that I can ensure accurate and up-to-date product descriptions.
US-39 - As a Product Staff, I want to create new product listings in the store, so that I can expand the product catalog and cater to diverse customer needs.
US-38 - As a Manager, I want to delete memberships that violate user agreements, so that I can maintain a safe and secure online environment.
US-37 - As a Manager, I want to set discounts for specific products, so that I can run targeted promotions and manage store inventory.
US-36 - As a Manager, I want to create and manage vouchers for promotions, so that I can attract new customers and encourage repeat business.
US-35 - As a Manager, I want to update membership details and privileges, so that I can create different membership tiers and offer customized benefits.
US-34 - As a Member, I want to make secure payments for my orders, so that I can complete transactions with confidence and peace of mind.
US-33 - As a Member, I want to report inappropriate posts or comments, so that I can contribute to a safe and positive online environment.
US-32 - As a Member, I want to submit a request for a refund on an order, so that I can return unwanted items in a hassle-free manner.
US-31 - As a Member, I want to initiate a chat with store staff for assistance, so that I can get real-time support and answers to my questions.
US-30 - As a Member, I want to view and interact with store feedback from other members, so that I can gain valuable insights and build a sense of community.
US-29 - As a Member, I want to post comments and reviews on products, so that I can share my experience and help other mothers make informed decisions.
US-28 - As a Member, I want to add vouchers to my order for discounts, so that I can save money on purchases.
US-27 - As a Member, I want to view my membership information, so that I can be informed about my privileges and information about them.
US-26 - As a Member, I want to track the status of my orders, so that I can stay informed about the delivery progress.
US-25 - As a Member, I want to view my complete order history, so that I can easily track past purchases and manage returns if needed.
US-24 - As a Member, I want to view and edit the contents of my shopping cart, so that I can make changes before finalizing my order.
US-23 - As a Member, I want to add products to my cart for purchase, so that I can conveniently collect the items I wish to buy.
US-22 - As a Guest, I want to mark products as favorites for later reference, so that I can easily revisit products that caught my attention.
US-21 - As a Guest, I want to search for specific products by name or category, so that I can quickly find the items I'm interested in.
US-20 - As a Guest, I want to browse the store and view products without creating an account, so that I can easily explore product offerings before committing to membership.
US-19 - As a Guest, I want to register to the web so that I can have access to various functions of it for further decisions
